8
1 (2) at least one (1) township;
2 all of which are participating units in the same fire protection
3 territory on the date the reorganization plan is finally adopted
4 under this chapter.
5 (b) The fiscal body of the designated unit may:
6 (1) establish an equipment replacement fund under
7 IC 36-8-19-8.5 and impose a property tax for the fund as
8 provided in IC 36-8-19-8.5; and
9 (2) take any other action under IC 36-8-19-8.5 that may be
