4 (2) Pension obligations existing as of January 1, 2028:
5 (A) may not be imposed on taxpayers that were not
6 responsible for payment of the pension obligations before
7 January 1, 2028; and
8 (B) must be paid by the taxpayers that were responsible for
9 payment of the pension obligations before January 1, 2028.
